        Douglas M. Baker, Jr.

    

Doug Baker is chairman of the board and chief executive officer of Ecolab Inc. Baker began his career with Ecolab in 1989, and has held key roles in marketing, sales and management in the U.S. and Europe.  In July 2004, Baker was named president and chief executive officer, and in May 2006, added chairman of the board to his duties. 











